    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为CloudNative_HelmChart项目创建一个甘特图，重点是展示包容性结束日期的处理方式。标题就用\"Inclusive end dates (CloudNative_HelmChart)\"吧。",
