    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，日期格式用YYYY-MM-DD，axisFormat用%d显示日期数字。inclusiveEndDates这个开关一定要加上，这是这个图的核心特性。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "dateFormat YYYY-MM-DD",
        "axisFormat %d",
        "inclusiveEndDates"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，基础配置已设置。现在我来添加Section1区域，里面放两个任务：第一个是\"2 Days\"，从2019-01-01开始，持续2天；第二个是\"Manual Date\"，同样从2019-01-01开始，但手动指定到2019-01-03结束。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Section1",
        "2 Days",
        "Manual Date",
        "2019-01-01",
        "2d",
        "2019-01-03"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，这两个任务我想对比一下：第一个用2d的相对时长，第二个用明确日期。在inclusiveEndDates模式下，2d的任务应该也是到1月3号结束对吧？因为1号、2号、3号都算在内。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "2d",
        "2019-01-03",
        "inclusiveEndDates"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，理解正确。2d表示包含起始日在内的2天，所以1月1日和2日？不对，让我再想想——inclusiveEndDates开启后，2d应该是1号到2号？还是您确认一下这个计算逻辑？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "2d",
        "inclusiveEndDates"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "实际上inclusiveEndDates影响的是明确日期指定的任务。2d这种相对时长不受它影响，就是简单的2天。但Manual Date那个任务，2019-01-03作为结束日期会被包含在内。两个任务最终都是3号结束，正好形成对比。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "2 Days",
        "Manual Date",
        "inclusiveEndDates",
        "2019-01-03"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，已调整完成。现在Section1里两个任务都正确配置：\"2 Days\"用2d相对时长，\"Manual Date\"用2019-01-01到2019-01-03的明确日期范围，inclusiveEndDates确保结束日被计入。图表可以渲染了。",
